Source: https://github.com/dexie/dexie.js/blob/master/test/rebalance.md

This section provides a textual visualization of a tree data structure undergoing common balancing operations. It demonstrates the process of inserting a new node, performing a rotation to maintain balance, and finally, the desired rebalanced state of the tree, illustrating the algorithmic steps involved in self-balancing trees.

```text
Tree:
        [63-71]
    (null)  [99-102]

Insert [90-92]:

        [63-71]
  (null)      [99-102]
          [90-92]    (null)

Rotation:
       [99-102]
  [63-72]       (null)
(null)   [90-92]

Rebalance root (as it SHOULD be):

          [90-92]
  [63-71]        [99-102]
(null) (null)  (null)  (null)
