### Reading Initial Bytes from a Blob using Slicing

Source: https://github.com/dexie/dexie.js/blob/master/addons/dexie-export-import/README.md

This snippet demonstrates how to read a small initial portion of a Blob without loading the entire file into memory. It uses the 'slice' method to create a new Blob containing only the first 100 bytes, which can then be read using a FileReader.

```js
const firstPart = blob.slice(0,100);
```
